title: Bloomberg Intelligence: Uber & Beyond Meat IPOs (Podcast)

description:
On this week's Bloomberg Intelligence podcast, Alix Steel and Paul Sweeney discuss initial public offerings from Uber Technologies Inc. and Beyond Meat Inc. Bloomberg Intelligence provides in-depth research and data on more than 2,000 companies and 130 industries. Hosts: Alix Steel and Paul Sweeney Producers: Richard Trueman and Madena Parwana
